- welder in fabrication shop (sparks, mask up/down contrast, industrial background)  
- plumber on emergency call (under sink, water mess, cramped indoor repair)  
- trucker at rest stop (cab interior, late-night fatigue, isolation)  
- oilfield or industrial worker (PPE, outdoor site, harsh conditions)  
- retail/service worker crossover (double-shift energy, uniform, break-room slump)  
- trade school student (classroom plus lab, tools laid out)  
